  "text": "Analytical techniques. During growth at steady state, cell filtrates were obtained by centrifuging culture samples (6000 g, 10 min at 4 uC) followed by filtration of the supernatant through 0.22 mm filters (Durapore, Millipore). Residual levels of amino acids and glucose were measured by methods described previously [CITATION_1] .",
